title: Starpoint Gemini Warlords GOG Version 1.0
description:
Here is the install files for Starpoint Gemini Warlords straight from GOG. There is no crack needed. If I manage to get the deluxe upgrade later I will do a separate post for those files.

Instructions:

Step 1: Use a program like 7-zip to extract the installer files to a folder on your PC.
Step 2: Run the the file setup_starpoint_gemini_warlords_1.000.1_(12207).exe to start the installer and follow the setup wizard.
Step 3: Run the game via the shortcuts created on the start menu and/or desktop.
Step 4: Enjoy! (or don't it's up to you)



Any questions feel free to ask. I will try to check the comments to help.

As it is zipped here is a list of the included files for transparency. I zipped it as to make it smaller and easier to download for those with a lesser internet connection.

setup_starpoint_gemini_warlords_1.000.1_(12207).exe
setup_starpoint_gemini_warlords_1.000.1_(12207)-1.bin
setup_starpoint_gemini_warlords_1.000.1_(12207)-2.bin

There will be some moments I will stop seeding due to my works VPN cutting it off
